trans-unit.source: Acts as the top of a two-level named hierarchy of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection"></xref> collections.
trans-unit.target: Pełni rolę początku dwupoziomowej hierarchii nazwanego elementu <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection"> </xref> kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: The RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection class is both a root-level <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collection and a container for a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Klasa RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection jest zarówno głównym poziomie <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>kolekcji i kontener dla <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection>kolekcji.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>

trans-unit.source: These collections allow you to create named groups of more <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collections, each containing individual named <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objects.
trans-unit.target: Te kolekcje, pozwala na tworzenie grupy o nazwie więcej <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>kolekcje, poszczególnych zawierającego o nazwie <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings>obiektów.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the profile features added to [!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/add/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)], see [NIB: ASP.NET Profile Properties](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/06a7bf4a-a5a2-462d-9793-c79063a2018d).
